### **4. 24_LivePlotGenerator**  
**Description:**  
A real-time charting tool using Matplotlib to visualize any numeric data stream.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LivePlotGenerator - Real-Time Visualization

LivePlotGenerator builds animated charts from incoming data. Ideal for sensor streams, simulations, or logs.

## Features
- Real-time line graphs  
- Customizable input stream  
- Pause/resume visualization  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_LivePlotGenerator.git
cd 24_LivePlotGenerator
python visualize.py
